{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"49263f4592","title":"邓小平在西楼会议上的发言摘录","origin":"《邓小平反革命修正主义言论文章汇编(第一集)》，首都红代会中国人民大学三红揪邓兵团，一九六七年五月十二日出版。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4966c5cc71","index":0,"year":1962,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"49263f4592"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f0e44655bb","name":"邓小平"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d847a5948e","type":"title","text":"邓小平在西楼会议上的发言摘录","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"c7d55b46c6","type":"authors","text":"邓小平","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"16330e3c90","type":"paragraph","text":"谈到如何控制劳动工资和亏损企业时，邓小平说：“财政、银行要卡死，不要怕工人打扁担，厂长打跑了，免得我们撤换。这样严格了，就可以逼他们搞经济核算。现在要恢复象一九五三年以前那样的制度。”","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"e75f81a2b3","type":"paragraph","text":"*    　　　　　　　*　　　　　　　    *","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"7f6bcdcdb5","type":"paragraph","text":"办法要得用，要少。如高级品。总之不能多，要搞真正捞到东西的。点子太多，作用不大。延期付款的买卖不能多做，否则积在一起，转不过来。办法有三条：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"de509c39f7","type":"paragraph","text":"1．根本办法，在于减人。主要表现在建设速度放慢。这不会得罪人，无非是对外名誉不好。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"1fecdbe77a","type":"paragraph","text":"2．真正抓点生活用品，回笼票子。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"5fd55b3c01","type":"paragraph","text":"3．制度搞严，漏洞堵死，措施要落实，能顶多少是多少。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"320c5a6a6d","type":"paragraph","text":"保经济作物，少而精，拿点粮食，如烟叶。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"15a94402e6","type":"paragraph","text":"*    　　　　　　　*　　　　　　　    *","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"ac586fba51","type":"paragraph","text":"现在要恢复到一九五四年那样，管得死死的，搞一段再说。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"aad0929c05","type":"paragraph","text":"几个办法：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"08f4172b12","type":"paragraph","text":"1．节约一切能够节约的资金，但钱不一定很多，可改变风气。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"fa9e8bfd87","type":"paragraph","text":"2．农村投放，过去剥削农民多(了)，这几年给农民是否多了。提价、退赔都过分了，再加上集市贸易更多了。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"fa6d895afe","type":"paragraph","text":"3．基本建设和生产的关系。可否两三年内基本停止建设，只有两种：①维持再生产；②保护工程。只搞这两项，连国防也可考虑停下来。把市场转过来，再来搞。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"a5fca4a4cd","type":"paragraph","text":"煤炭、矿山、森林，有色金属缺门不能停。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"5d0a5f3f1b","type":"paragraph","text":"生产，首先搞零配件，拖拉机应该首先要搞零配件。主要搞生活资料。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"4dd4cb199a","type":"paragraph","text":"*    　　　　　　　*　　　　　　　    *","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"26683eed76","type":"paragraph","text":"有人谈到财政、银行、商业正在搞制度时，邓小平插话说：“可以考虑，生产多一点，物价提×％，工资提×％，但关键在工业品。”","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"629e962184","type":"paragraph","text":"刘少奇谈到基建除了某些必要的外都停止时，邓小平插话说：“国防基建，也要紧缩一下。”","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"},{"id":"6e6043d6ea","type":"appellation","text":"","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592"}],"page":{"id":"2a76af0859","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49263f4592","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}